    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Re ''Bagging Eternal Plastics'' (editorial, April 15):</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Re ''Bagging Eternal Plastics'' (editorial, April 15):</p>
        <p>I was recently in France, where stores have stopped giving out plastic bags with purchases. I'm sick of seeing plastic bags flying down the streets, stuck in trees and bushes, and floating in the waterways.</p>
        <p>We have adopted the French model in our home, taking our own bags, and it works very well. I mean, what did people do before plastic bags?</p>
        <p>Nathalie Cunningham  North Hollywood, Calif.  April 15, 2007</p>
      </block>
